Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:12.38,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,398)}For you, who have passed the first exam, I will admit that you are bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:18.80,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348,395)}But whether that brightness is from a gemstone or just a pebble is hard to tell at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:22.62,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,That again, Erica?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:27.00,Overlap,,0,0,0,,And so, by doing lessons, we want you to learn the basics together...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:25.93,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,It's times like this that I need to be a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:28.81,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you get noticed easier in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:33.06,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Especially... ninja and companions over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:33.94,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:35.98,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Never be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:41.61,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh, he saw us. He must be a saru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:41.61,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(336,69)}Erica shortened "sarumono", which means a clever, strong person with no weaknesses, to "saru" which means monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:43.62,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Not saru, it's sarumono.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:49.12,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,380)}Stand up, everyone. Do not daydream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:54.63,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I am in charge of dance and body design, Yamashiro Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:57.84,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Just because you are candidates, does not mean I will go easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:01.68,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I will cut those who cannot keep up without mercy, so I expect you to behave accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:02.59,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Understod.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:08.43,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. If you try your best, she'll surely look at you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.18,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:11.23,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.23,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.77,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You have some guts to be talking during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.98,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,N-No, it wasn't like-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:19.15,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Don't answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:19.99,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:23.74,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Now we will begin with some warm-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:28.49,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You! Bad posture. Stretch out your back a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:32.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,No, don't push your chest out, stretch your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.21,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,S-So strenuous...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:35.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Don't relax your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.21,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Keep your face up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:43.01,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,And done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:45.68,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I can't take anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:47.60,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Five minute break!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:54.98,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Your arms and legs are long so you'll look better on stage. Keep focusing on that in your dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:55.98,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:58.77,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What's with that? She was born that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:01.07,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Foreigners are cheaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:02.32,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Good for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:04.15,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,381)}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:10.66,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I'm in charge of everyone's voice training and teaching music theory. My name is Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:14.12,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,So, let us practice singing to match notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:15.17,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.71,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,A Little clearer, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:27.89,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:36.81,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You, to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:38.11,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:41.15,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,It's not about being as loud as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.53,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Your voice should come from your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:46.07,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,O-kay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:49.53,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hi everyone, we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:54.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I am Danny Yamaguchi, in charge of makeup and cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:58.13,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Let's begin by learning the basics of makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:04:59.84,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I need a model...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.42,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Here! I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:10.47,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hmm, let's see. Your face is too clear-cut, so it'll change your face too drastically. No good in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.18,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Someone who has more of a shoyu taste would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:15.93,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What about Haruka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:22.11,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What? No way. That makes the difference between me and the foreigner too apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.86,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.74,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're the funny girl from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:33.08,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hmmm... you have too much, and in a different way, so it might be a bit too difficult, even for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.54,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hey, what should we do for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.17,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,There was a good place somewhere near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.55,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:53.64,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Amazing. Did you make all that by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:54.56,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.93,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Obento's are best made at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.06,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Do you want to eat some?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:03.52,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Give me some! Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.28,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:08.15,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yay! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:11.91,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,So good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:14.74,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Don't you cook your own food?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:19.37,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,A little. But not like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.38,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh, looks colorful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:23.54,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.55,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Why don't you eat some too, Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.72,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Ah, no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.63,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.80,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh no. I'm trying to wring my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:37.85,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh right, I wouldn't be able to walk if I ate more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.89,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:44.19,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh Erica, can you teach me some cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.19,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Eh, Cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:51.57,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I thought I'd want to visit your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:55.45,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll be waiting. Please feel free to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.24,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yay, score.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:07:00.62,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're supposed to eat that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:04.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,The first lesson this afternoon looks a little rough for a full stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:06.38,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right...
