Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:12.55,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:16.51,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I slept a lot yesterday because it was the Harbor Opening Anniversary, so I feel great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:16.51,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(346,61)}The anniversary for opening harbors for international trade is July 1, 1859. However, the anniversary is celebrated on June 2nd,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.76,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(346,60)}which corresponds to July 1st on the lunar calendar the Japanese were following at the time. Most schools do not have classes on this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.14,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Don't screw up like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.85,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What? I didn't screw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:24.73,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.98,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Erica, you're Takumi's older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:27.81,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:29.52,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.44,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh? Takumi's, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.61,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hey, who's Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.99,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What? From Third Sence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.49,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Third Sence...? Third Sence...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:55.63,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Are you serious? Takumi's? I'm so envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:59.22,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hey, Erica-san, mind if I visit your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:03.76,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,We're both candidates, right? And of course Takumi is going to be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.06,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh sure. You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.81,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Then, Fuyumi, make sure you do everything in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.65,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah, I have to do something on Sunday...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:14.27,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You're coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:17.07,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Eh, oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:22.37,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Erica, I want to go too. You said you'd teach me how to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:28.04,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Then I'll be waiting with a feast, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:29.62,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.13,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Then I'll come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:34.88,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What? You said you were dieting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:39.43,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I never said I'd go eat... and why are you telling everyone that I'm dieting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:42.30,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:48.64,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Miki-san... is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:57.36,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.65,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:01.99,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:09.25,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh? This is a song by Third Sence... Who's phone is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:11.83,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,It's gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.68,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Takumi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:54.96,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,Hey, sis, do you think I can make friends where we're about to go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:58.21,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:11:59.84,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:03.38,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's the country mama was born in, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:14.44,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,Whoa. Such a cool color, Erica.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:15.94,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:18.52,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,Foreigners are so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.36,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,Her sense is so peculiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.28,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because she's a foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:27.07,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,Even if she didn't want to, she'll stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:31.00,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:32.00,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:36.38,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,We're a little different. That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:42.01,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,And about that invitation, I think I'll accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:44.47,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,Huh? Which invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:58.56,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,Working today too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.65,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and then we have a party at a member's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:06.07,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,I might be a little late. They'll insist that I stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:07.45,Main Style Lemon Angel_2,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:25.09,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takumi... I can finally...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:32.10,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hello? Takumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.56,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.02,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:44.07,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Okay. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:51.45,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.45,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hey, Erica!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:55.62,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.92,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Wow, pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:01.84,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,After all, it is a foreigner's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.88,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Say, where's Takumi? Bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:08.93,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,No, he said he had to stay at the set longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:13.76,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I made a lot to eat, so please enjoy yourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:19.48,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Huh? Takumi isn't here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:21.44,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.73,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:25.23,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Haruka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:27.24,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Could the outfield please shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:29.99,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Erica!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:33.99,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,If your brother Takumi isn't here, you're just an opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:37.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What a waste of time to go to a house that's owned by someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:43.46,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,B-But we got to know each other because we got chosen as candidates. Couldn't we at least enjoy a meal together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:48.38,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What? If we eat something weird like this, it's obviously not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:51.97,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go as far as poison, but maybe you mixed in some laxatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.81,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You aren't Japanese in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.89,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:14:59.89,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Haruka-chan, that's going too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:03.81,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Fuyumi and I came here instead of going to a relative's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:07.40,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Haruka-chan, there was a funeral today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:10.45,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You're evil, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:13.99,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You're trying to get into Lemon Angel with your brother's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:18.00,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,And even trying to make other candidates drop out by making them eat food mixed with laxatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:23.08,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I pity Takumi for having this parasite of an older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:25.71,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Erica!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:29.26,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Oh? Was I on to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:33.64,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You took advantage, didn't you? Of Takumi not being around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:37.39,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.27,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Heh, so naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:40.52,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:46.82,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,If you think you can win by crushing others, you have a lot to learn... about those in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:49.86,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Heh, you're just a second rate singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:57.08,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Erica?! Where are you? Erica!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.33,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Erica?! Erica?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:14.93,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:16.97,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,No... Not a trace-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.27,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm soaking wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:31.40,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I can't keep this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:37.62,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Let's get going. If we don't find her quickly, we'll catch a cold... both Erica and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:42.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But why am I not in that list?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:45.08,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Do I even have to answer that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:46.75,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.34,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Erica!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.46,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Erica!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:57.47,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Erica! Where are you, Erica?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:17:00.10,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Erica!! Erica!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:06.98,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:11.48,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Ah! There she is!
