Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:16.52,Betétdal_HUN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(359,67)}The feeling that I have for others never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:30.56,Betétdal_HUN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(359,67)}Smiles anywhere in the world come with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:42.36,Betétdal_HUN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(359,67)}Because I realized that I am in the bottom of the cleft.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.09,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Erica.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:31.25,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353,382)}Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:36.59,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Please don't come near me....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:41.22,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,It's just a cycle of the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:44.48,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I thought I really found the place where I belong this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:51.19,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,In Brazil and in Japan, I was a foreigner. And now Takumi found his own place...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.32,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,So I thought I needed to find one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.66,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I met Tomo and other friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:18:02.17,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,that wanted to be Lemon Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:08.17,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Occassionally, people looked at me like a foreigner, but I kept thinking these people were different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:11.96,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,But everyone was after Takumi and not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:14.34,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,That's wrong, Erica. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:21.68,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,It's not wrong. Even you... what should I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:25.39,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just quit then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:32.31,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I can see why you weren't competitive now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:38.20,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,In other words, you just wanted a friendly club out of Lemon Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:44.28,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Quit playing games! We didn't come to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:48.33,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Everyone's a rival, like myself, even Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:51.54,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Everyone's putting themselves on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:57.92,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,We're all trying to be the last one standing after giving everything we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.09,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,It's because we have that resolve that we can be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:05.35,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,And aren't you forgetting something? We can only be together until the last audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:08.43,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,After that, there are two paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:14.02,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,The winners, who attain a place to shine with other comrades, and the losers, who lose everything and disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:19.11,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What about you? Are you prepared to give everything you have to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.09,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.49,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I want to sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:30.50,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'll pass the audition, but I want to try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:35.54,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,We can be comrades, right, Erica?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:42.59,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,We can become friends who sing together, dance together, compete against each other, but encourage each other, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:48.47,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,We have to! Let's be. Because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:51.44,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Tomo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:53.56,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Let's sing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:04.11,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:07.28,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,What I really want is still ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:12.08,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Tomo, Saya, I will do my best, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:15.75,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I'll give more effort and make my way to Lemon Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:21.76,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,And I will be your true rival. Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.34,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:30.56,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,And why am I giving advice to a rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:34.02,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we found you, Erica.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:37.98,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Tomo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:42.57,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,E-Erica?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:44.15,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:49.03,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,E-Erica, you're strangling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:51.95,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's people watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:55.92,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.38,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:04.97,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,So good...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:07.80,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you eating my share too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.97,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Because it's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:11.64,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:14.18,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be taking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:17.31,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Wha?! Now you're being spiteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:20.77,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,There's still a lot left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:21.98,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:29.20,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takumi, I found a place... truly just for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:53.77,Main Style Lemon Angel,,0,0,0,,I will surpass you. And then... defeat you.
